definitions.definition: ( botany ) A member of the genus Prunella of herbaceous plants , the allheals . [from 16th c.]

main_definition: ( botany ) A member of the genus Prunella of herbaceous plants , the allheals . [from 16th c.]

definitions.definition: ( obsolete , medicine ) Any of various diseases characterised by inflammation of the mouth or throat . [17th–18th c.]

definitions.definition: A smooth worsted or silk fabric, generally black, formerly used for making shoes and clergymen's gowns.
